
BNF for Lab08 Expression Grammar

list: e | list stmt '\n' 
stmt: expr 
expr: term  | expr - term  | expr + term  
term: fact | term * fact | term / fact 
fact: id | (expr) | -fact
id:  a | b | c 


Example AST for input: 
a * -(b+c) / a 

divides(times(a,negative((plus(b,c)))),a)

In tree form:

          divides
          /      \
     times        a
    /     \
   a    negative
          |
        plus
        /  \
       b    c


Rightmost Derivation Parse tree for:   
a * -(b+c) / a 

              list
             /    \
           list   stmt
           |        |
           e       expr
                     |
                    term
                 /   |  \
            term     /  fact
           / | \         |
       term  *  fact     a 
        |       / \ 
        a      -  fact
                  / | \
                 ( expr )
                  / | \
                 b  +  c

  
